column2: an A.M. Eatery////Aaron brought us the Sinful pancake as an appetizer and it was AMAZING! I got the OMG French toast with no coconut and it was super yummy! My friends got the Benny Goodman
column4: and pancake of the day. They loved the first two. The winter harvest was a "light breakfast" according to her. The strawberry Bliss was a miss (in our opinion). It was a weird mixture of flavors and it wasn't nearly as good as the Sinful pancake that we started with.
